{"about_the_game":"Misty Islands is an action-packed survival adventure game. After a mysterious shipwreck, you find yourself stranded on a deserted island. You must gather resources, build a home, craft equipment, and explore the islands. You must make the most of everything around you to survive and uncover the truth.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Island Survival</h2>Hunger constantly threatens you, and you must ensure an adequate food supply through fishing, hunting, or gathering.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561370/extras/fishing.gif?t=1737595745\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Resource Gathering</h2>All resources need to be collected, crafted, and processed by youself. Fortunately, the islands are scattered with useful resources.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561370/extras/gathering.gif?t=1737595745\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Base Building</h2>Utilize the limited resources on the deserted island to build a sanctuary. Crafting, forging, cooking...most importantly, you'll have a place to call home.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561370/extras/home.gif?t=1737595745\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Adventures</h2>Misty Islands conceal numerous relics and caves, from beast lairs to bottomless abysses. Crafting powerful weapons and armor will allow you to easily obtain hidden treasures.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561370/extras/fight.gif?t=1737595745\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Naval Battles</h2>Navigate the islands, investigate the wreckage of fleets, search for survivors or victims, gather clues from them, and uncover the truth behind the shipwreck.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561370/extras/Sea.gif?t=1737595745\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Challanges</h2>Each island is controlled by a powerful force. Conquer them, face various challenges and threats, and eventually become the dominator of the misty islands.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561370/extras/boss.gif?t=1737595745\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561370/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737595745","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561370/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737595745","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561370/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737595745","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561370/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737595745","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"Cartoon Violence"},"demos":[{"appid":2661910,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<h1>Discord</h1><p></p><br><h1>Wishlist now!</h1><p><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561370/extras/wishlist_textless.gif?t=1737595745\" /></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Misty Islands is an action-packed survival adventure game. After a mysterious shipwreck, you find yourself stranded on a deserted island. You must gather resources, build a home, craft equipment, and explore the islands. You must make the most of everything around you to survive and uncover the truth.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Island Survival</h2>Hunger constantly threatens you, and you must ensure an adequate food supply through fishing, hunting, or gathering.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561370/extras/fishing.gif?t=1737595745\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Resource Gathering</h2>All resources need to be collected, crafted, and processed by youself. Fortunately, the islands are scattered with useful resources.